Package dsp

Interface Summary
InfoListener This interface defines the method which will be called, if a SignalEvent is sent to the class which implement this interface.
SignalListener This interface defines the method which will be called, if a SignalEvent is sent to the class which implement this interface.
 

Class Summary
Alg Abstract class.
AlgController The AlgController handles the algorithm.
AlgLinearkombiner The AlgLinearkombiner is the main algorithm of this project.
AlgNew Additional Algorithmus without any logic.
AlgRLC The AlgRLC is one of the two algorithm of this project.
Application This is the Main / Start Application This class is a part of the Project "RLC-Messbruecke fuer 5 Franken" University of Applied Sciences Lucerne - Switzerland
FreqSweep This class generates the frequency-sweep over the specified frequency array.
Hilbert Transforms the signal in a real and a imaginary signal.
InfoEvent This class represents a EventObject, which is sent from SignalProviders to the listeners.
InfoProvider This abstract class represents the base functionality for all classes which provides signals.
SignalEvent This class represents a EventObject, which is sent from SignalProviders to the listeners.
SignalEventBuffer The SignalEventBuffer is the part bedween the Input and the TraceCanvas It receive and buffers the samples from the input.
SignalProvider This abstract class represents the base functionality for all classes which provides signals.
Sinusgenerator Generates the sinussignal used from the output.
